Ndxf3+ 18. gxf3 Nd3 19. Bxd3 Bxd3 20. Be7 Bxc4 21. d6 Bb5 $15) 12... Qxe2 13.
Bh6 $5 {Otherwise Black would be just better.} Qe4 14. Qxe4 Nxe4 15. Rfe1 f5
16. Bf4 Nd7 17. Nh4 {Not a great square for the knight, but otherwise the
knight on e4 would be hard to tolerate.} g6 18. f3 Nxc3 19. a4 {This fails to
