$1 20. Kf1 b5 $1 21. axb5 Nb6 22. Bd2 (22. Bxd6 Nxc4 $19) 22... Nca4 23. Rxe8+
Rxe8 24. Bc1 a6 25. bxa6 Ra8 26. Bf4 Rxa6 27. Bxd6 Nxc4 28. Bf4 Kf7 $11) 9...
Bxc3+ 10. bxc3 e5 {One of the possible plans.} ({In practice, Black usually
plays} 10... exd5 11. exd5 Bg4 12. O-O Nbd7 13. Rae1 $5 {This odd move is
forced due to certain concrete circumstances.} (13. Rfe1 Rfe8 14. h3 Bh5 15.
