15. Qxd5 Nxb4 16. Qd2 Nd5 17. Bd4 Re8 $17) 9... O-O {[%cal Gd7d5] Threatening .
..d7-d5.} 10. b4 d5 $5 {Nevertheless!} 11. c5 e5 {Taking full advantage of
