26. Bb2 Ng5 $19) (22. bxc5 Bd5 $17) 22... Qf6 23. Qxc7 Bd5 24. fxe6 Rf5 25. Be2
Qxe6 26. Bb2 Rg5 $3 {[%csl Gg7] Defending g7 in order to unpin the knight.} 27.
